{"about_the_game":"Use decorations, lights, sounds and more to design a haunted house then open it for guests and see how they react. Guests will leave reviews and if done well enough you'll eventually unlock different areas and more decorations as you become the ultimate haunted house builder.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Many things are available to build your haunted house including lights you can customize via direction and color, speakers to play scary laughs or thunder ambiance, animatronics, posable monsters, trigger pads and more.<br></li><li>Several different decorations including old furniture, paintings, lamps, and monsters.<br></li><li>Some decorations will need power and others will require a trigger for full effect so generators and motion detectors will need to be strategically placed.<br></li><li>Design walls, ceilings, and floors by changing their materials and making them into doors or removing them altogether for more room.<br></li><li>Guests will react to different things, might flee if too spooked and will leave reviews detailing their haunted house experience.<br></li><li>Some guests are picky and will need tailored decorations to get a good review.<br></li><li>Unlock strange and unusual decorations and areas as you progress.<br></li><li>Unique locations like abandoned areas or forests.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Mission Complete","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2626180/2d5e31da7b13b14e87d4c94acaff5036c4fe769d.jpg"},{"name":"Game Cart","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2626180/8a0e4c75d515f81a5be5c3ed8eedf87db5083064.jpg"},{"name":"I Ran (Ran so far away)","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2626180/aaa8f18f693cb04e075a5432d65ed54e34374e5c.jpg"},{"name":"Duck?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2626180/f3851f562565c97fcbfca